{"tid":1090976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命車禍】老翁東區走廊行走 遭車撞死　","createTime":"2019-04-04T00:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T01:15:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54bc197387a9bc0045c58622fec605a87009fae6","tid":1090976,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:05:44.000Z","msg":"【奪命車禍】老翁東區走廊行走 遭車撞死　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190404/59447663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F59447663&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5HHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=d6f47218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F59447663&h=986adbfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190404/59447663</a><br />\n<br />\n東區走廊發生致命車禍，凌晨4時47分，警方接獲駕駛人士報案，指一名老翁在東行線行走，約10分鐘後，懷疑老翁被車撞倒，倒卧近和富中心快線路面。消防及救護員到場救援，證實已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，當時有兩輛的士駛經，發現老翁倒卧地上，的士司機立即將車停下，以防老翁再被車輾過。警方到場調查，發現一個黑色倒後鏡，相信是撞倒老翁的車輛遺下，老翁身體並有輾過痕迹，器官外露，路面遺下血迹，不排除被車撞倒後，再被其它車輾過，涉事車輛不顧而去。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓王75歲，警方撿獲遺物，包括身份證、銀行簿、收音機、波鞋及外套等。警方封鎖現場三條行車線調查，剩下一條線行車，交通一度擠塞。警方正追緝涉事車輛下落。"},{"pid":"5ba151ab82ca99b693b03a0736373c9fce2b150a","tid":1090976,"uid":49664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"認知障礙"},{"pid":"a88a149e709b576a42d940358b41091471909984","tid":1090976,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5d6f4ee551e27751155bffed18a89127730fa3","tid":1090976,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:01:26.000Z","msg":"又累死司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d15839eb313ade8e28a662f34c9fae9a311e9e","tid":1090976,